#Birthday Celebration Website - Joy Connection

> **A creative open-source interactive website** that helps you organize, remember, and share memorable birthday moments in a fun and unique way! From countdown timers, interactive 3D birthday cakes with blowable candles, to photo/video albums, mini-games, community chat, and seasonal interfaces - all creating an unforgettable experience!

